Second Department,

November, 1950.

(November 1, 1950.) Ann Gans, Respondent, v. Albert Gans, Appellant.

Motion referred to the court that rendered the decision. Present — ■ Nolan, P. J., Carswell, Sneed, Wenzel and MaeCrate, JJ. Motion to vacate order of July 7, 1950 (ante, p. 930), and for other relief denied, without costs. Present — Nolan, P. J., Adel, Wenzel and MaeCrate, JJ.
